OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783961288
OL,3,CFire disrupts services at Stratford as
OL,4,Cbrigade warns of wildfire risk
OL,6,FThere is major disruption at Stratford
OL,7,FStation after a fire near the track on
OL,8,FFriday evening.
OL,10,FPolice responded to reports of a blaze
OL,11,Fnear the line around 7pm and confirmed
OL,12,Fthat firefighters were on the scene.
OL,14,FA statement from London Fire Brigade
OL,15,Fon Friday evening said: "Firefighters
OL,16,Fare currently in attendance at a fire
OL,17,Finvolving shrubbery near the railway
OL,18,Fline at _Stratford train station.
OL,20,F"The station has been temporarily
OL,21,Fclosed. More to follow."
OL,26,@wD@YOU|D@AOU}D@XO]
