PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783961288
OL,3,CFire disrupts services at Stratford as
OL,4,Cbrigade warns of wildfire risk
OL,6,FAs a result, Transport for London is
OL,7,Freported severe delays on the
OL,8,FElizabeth, Mildmay and Jubilee lines.
OL,10,FThe blaze came as London Fire Brigade
OL,11,Fwarned of the risk of wildfires during
OL,12,Fthe heatwave this weekend.
OL,14,FThe latest assessments show the risk
OL,15,Fin London will grow from "elevated" to
OL,16,F"extreme" from Saturday to Monday,
OL,17,Fdriven by factors like prolonged dry
OL,18,Fweather, heat and wind speed.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUwD@cO]xD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
