PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783961288
OL,3,CFire disrupts services at Stratford as
OL,4,Cbrigade warns of wildfire risk
OL,6,FLFB assistant commissioner Tom Goodall
OL,7,Fsaid: "We want everyone across the
OL,8,Fcity to enjoy the continuing heatwave
OL,9,Fbut this must be done responsibly.
OL,11,F"The latest wildfire risk assessment
OL,12,Findicates that if grass fires were to
OL,13,Fbreak out, the chance of them
OL,14,Fspreading more rapidly due to the
OL,15,Fweather conditions is greater.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
