FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783961288
OL,3,CFire disrupts services at Stratford as
OL,4,Cbrigade warns of wildfire risk
OL,6,F"With so many of London's parks and
OL,7,Fopen spaces close to properties and
OL,8,Fcommunities, it is vital the public
OL,9,Ftake as much care as possible to
OL,10,Fprevent these fires starting in the
OL,11,Ffirst place. We have seen first-hand
OL,12,Fin London, as well as around the
OL,13,Fworld, just how devastating the impact
OL,14,Fwildfires can have on livelihoods.
OL,16,F"That means no disposable barbecues in
OL,17,Fparks and open spaces, taking rubbish
OL,18,Fhome with you if no bins are available
OL,19,Fand ensuring your cigarettes are
OL,20,Fdiscarded of properly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
