OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783961288
OL,3,CFire disrupts services at Stratford as
OL,4,Cbrigade warns of wildfire risk
OL,6,F"If you're having a barbecue at home,
OL,7,Fmake sure it is on level ground and
OL,8,Faway from decking, fences, trees and
OL,9,Fbalconies."
OL,11,FThe Metropolitan Police is concerned
OL,12,Fabout excessive calls, with England
OL,13,Fset to play Norway in a quarter-final
OL,14,Fof the Fifa World Cup on Saturday
OL,15,Fnight.
OL,17,FThe Met has urged people to avoid
OL,18,Fgetting in touch for non-emergencies
OL,19,Famid a surge in 999 calls during the
OL,20,Fhot weather.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]
