OL,3,CFire disrupts services at Stratford as
OL,4,Cbrigade warns of wildfire risk
OL,6,FForecasters have said areas of England
OL,7,Fand Wales will continue to exceed 30C
OL,8,Fthroughout the weekend and into next
OL,9,Fweek.
